1. *Čim* se vratila, počela je da radi. (As soon as she returned, she started working.)
2. Spremila sam se *čim* je počelo da sviće. (I got ready as soon as it started getting light.)
3. *Čim* je ona ušla, svi su zastali. (As soon as she entered, everybody stopped.)
4. *Čim* završiš, možeš da odeš. (Once you finish, you can go.)
5. *Čim* smo krenuli, počela je da se tuče. (As soon as we started, it began to rain.)